Make sure you search in the USD, then USDT (just USDT if using website) search field. \n\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Once you\u2019ve found the coin, change the dropdown from \u2018Limit\u2019 to \u2018Market\u2019. This allows you to buy really quickly at the best possible price. \n\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Choose 25-100% to decide what % of your USDT you want to invest (the more you invest, the high the returns) and hit BUY!\n\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Wait a few minutes whilst our pump attracts outside investors, then SELL for profit using LIMIT SELL. Limit Sell means you can choose the price you wish to sell at.
